SELECT MIN(t.title) AS complete_downey_ironman_movie
FROM random_complete_cast_1 AS cc,
   random_comp_cast_type_1 AS cct1,
   random_comp_cast_type_1 AS cct2,
   random_char_name_1 AS chn,
   random_cast_info_1 AS ci,
   random_keyword_1 AS k,
   random_kind_type_1 AS kt,
   random_movie_keyword_1 AS mk,
   random_name_1 AS n,
   random_title_1 AS t
WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id
AND t.id = mk.movie_id
AND t.id = ci.movie_id
AND t.id = cc.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
AND n.id = ci.person_id
AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
AND cct1.kind = '@param0'
AND cct2.kind LIKE '@param1'
AND chn.name NOT LIKE '@param2'
AND (chn.name LIKE '@param3' OR chn.name LIKE '@param4')
AND k.keyword IN ('@param5')
AND kt.kind = '@param6'
AND t.production_year > @param7;
